data.description: Updated 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home on half an acre +/- lot in the coveted Plantation Subdivision and zoned to BHISD!!! The homes layout is perfect for entertaining with the kitchen completely open to the living room and eating areas AND a large covered back patio facing a recently re-surfaced pool and spa! It doesn't get much better than that! There is also a 12’, extra large access gate on the side fence, allowing large ATVs, boats and other toys to be parked discreetly in the backyard, out of view from the street!  The neighborhood offers a private boat ramp leading to the trinity bay and boat dock, perfect for fishing! Call to schedule your private showing today!
